When You Walk In, You Are Greeted With A Large 2 Story Foyer Open to Upstairs With A Formal Dining Room On One Side & Form Living Room On The Other. Laminate Flooring Throughout The Downstairs And Carpet Upstairs.  Bedroom 4 Is Located Downstairs With A Full Bathroom.  The Kitchen Has Received Some Updates To Lighting Fixtures To Personalize This Home.  Upstairs Is The Perfect Area For A Game Loft.  Laundry Room Is Located Upstairs For Convenience.  WOW! You Have To See The Master Bedroom! Large Master Bathroom With Separate Shower And Garden Tub.  Additional 2 Bedrooms And Full Bathroom Upstairs.  Large Fenced In Backyard With A Nicely Built Deck. Take A Look And Move To Huntington Today! Extremely Motivated Sellers, Bring All Offers!
